# Motion And Accessibility

## Reduced motion

- Use `useReducedMotion()` from Framer Motion (see `float-wrap.tsx`) to disable or simplify animations when the user prefers reduced motion.

## Performance

- Avoid layout shift from animated elements; reserve space where floats/phones animate.
- Prefer `transform` and `opacity` over layout-triggering properties.

## Scope

- Marketing motion lives under `src/components/marketing/phones/` and related section wrappers — do not add gratuitous motion to forms or critical CTAs.
